{"tid":370161,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「戒丁」 適當戒色 有效提升專注力，創意，體力，異性吸引力","createTime":"2017-08-23T00:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T04:56:49.000Z","uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72481771e71db5e6426e690d102bf101724ab503","tid":370161,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"咩叫適當戒色？<br />\n量化解釋，就係最多每星期1次 <br />\n唔止係打丁，連性交都計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n根據醫師林瀛洲說「禁欲時體內睪固酮濃度高，會增加體能爆發力」<br />\n睪固酮係人體分泌的壓力荷爾蒙<br />\n它刺激肌肉、骨骼、皮膚、性器官等發展。<br />\n睪固酮引發肌肉的增加、性器官的生長、骨骼的形成、更低沉的聲音，以及更旺盛的活力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://roguehealthandfitness.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/testosterone-molecules-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Froguehealthandfitness.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Ftestosterone-molecules-1.jpg&h=4896caaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://herbolab.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Normal-Testosterone.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fherbolab.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FNormal-Testosterone.jpg&h=7b1079f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為男人每射一次精，都會好傷元氣<br />\n會令男性體內既睪固酮含量下降<br />\n要抖最少要三日先可以回復元氣<br />\n要提升回復返男性體內既睪固酮含量，<br />\n林醫師說「運動可以提升睪固酮」<br />\n<br />\n小弟建議5天工作周打工仔既大家<br />\n可考慮星期五晚做約囡囡做性事／睇AV打丁抒發下壓力<br />\n然後星期六，日出下街，做下運動，訓好，食好，休息夠<br />\n以作回復完美體態，逐步回升精神, 專注力, 精力, 活力, 吸引力, 魅力 <br />\n以提升星期一至五既工作表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n形成一個良性循環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0c319206b850fac6727d6c83697803830b3ba4","tid":370161,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"齋睇片又點計法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e604ffb9718c4d9f974094983184a540ab7287da","tid":370161,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"你做起<br />\n包個膠嚟睇吓先"},